title: Rethinking Work: Are You Ready to Take Charge?
description:
Rethinking Work: Are You Ready to Take Charge?
Intercultural Press | 2007 | ISBN: 0891062300 | 168 pages | PDF | 1 MB

On any given day, more than 4 million Americans job search online. And regardless of age or profession--from Boomers to Gen Y's--today's financially encumbered and emotionally conflicted workers are looking for more than money as they pursue something new, better, different.
